name: The Colour Out of Oz
description: Venture into the worlds of both L. Frank Baum and H.P. Lovecraft as you attempt to expel the Colour from Earth with the assistance of the wonderous creatures from the Land of Oz. You will need all the help you can get as the Colour rapidly warps the world around it. Is there truly a way to stop the alien corruption? Or is Oz simply ground zero for the doom of Earth? Keep your wits and well-being as you fight to drive the Colour back into space!
